extends layout/main-layout

block styles
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css")

block scripts
    script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js")
    script(src="/scripts/slider.js") 

block content
    .h-50vh.flex.items-center
        div.container
            .max-w-md
                h1.text-6xl.font-medium.tracking-wider= mainpage.mainTitle
            .my-14
                a.btn(href='/arabalar') Araçlarımız
    .w-full.pt-50vh.pb-6.bg-gradient-to-r.from-gray-500.to-gray-800.drop-shadow-2xl.relative
        .car.-top-96.right-20.absolute.h-50vh
            img(class='xl:h-600px 2xl:h-800px' src='/images/car.webp')
        .container.relative
            h1.title.text-white.pb-16.text-4xl= mainpage.carsTitle 
            .swiper.mySwiper.p-2
                .swiper-wrapper.mb-12
                    each car in cars
                        .swiper-slide.card
                            .card-content
                                .card-img-box
                                    img.card-img(src=`/cms/assets/${car.img}?format=webp` alt='')
                                .card-text-box
                                    h1.card-text= `${car.Km} KM'DE`
                                    p İstanbul
                                .card-text-box
                                    p.card-price= `${car.Fiyat} TL`
            .swiper-button-next.next.text-blue-700
            .swiper-button-prev.prev
            .swiper-pagination
    .container
        .aboutme.flex.justify-between.items-center.my-36
            .about-img.w-500.h-96.bg-gradient-to-r.from-gray-500.to-gray-800.relative.rounded-3xl
                img.absolute.w-full.h-full.bg-cover.-top-12.-right-12.rounded-3xl(src=`/cms/assets/${mainpage.aboutImg}?format=webp` alt='')
            .max-w-2xl.flex-1
                h1.title.text-4xl.text-blue-700.pb-3= layoutData.about.baslik
                p.text-base.text-gray-700.leading-7.pb-4!= layoutData.about.summary
                .my-5
                    a.btn(href='/hakkimizda') Daha Fazla
        .w-full.flex.justify-center.text-center.mb-14
            h1.tag2.font-light.tracking-widest.text-1xl= mainpage.experianceTitle
        .values.items-stretch.my-30
            .col1
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl &Scedil;effafl&imath;k
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | M&uuml;&scedil;terilerimize kar&scedil;&imath; hi&ccedil;bir s&uuml;rpriz ya&scedil;atmadan her zaman a&ccedil;&imath;k
                        | ve d&uuml;r&uuml;st davran&imath;r&imath;z.
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl Kolayl&imath;k
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | M&uuml;&scedil;terilerimizle net bir ileti&scedil;im kurarak t&uuml;m s&uuml;recimizi
                        | anlamalar&imath;n&imath; sa&gbreve;l&imath;yoruz.
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl Modernlik
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | Devrim niteli&gbreve;indeki i&scedil; modelimizde m&uuml;&scedil;terilerimiz her zaman
                        | &ouml;nceliklidir. Bu bize sundu&gbreve;umuz deneyimleri herkes i&ccedil;in
                        | ki&scedil;iselle&scedil;tirme ve h&imath;zl&imath; hareket etme imkan&imath; sa&gbreve;lar.
            img(src='/images/car2.png' alt='' width="100%")#car-img
            .col2
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl Birliktelik
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | M&uuml;&scedil;terilerimiz ortaklar&imath;m&imath;zd&imath;r. T&uuml;m ara&ccedil; al&imath;&scedil; ve sat&imath;&scedil;
                        | s&uuml;re&ccedil;lerinde her t&uuml;rl&uuml; destek ihtiyac&imath;n&imath;z i&ccedil;in buraday&imath;z.
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl G&uuml;vence
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | AgiCars sizin yan&imath;n&imath;zda. Herkesin sorunsuz bir &scedil;ekilde ikinci el
                        | arac&imath;n&imath; satabilmesi en b&uuml;y&uuml;k hedefimiz.
                div
                    .flex.items-center
                        .flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-blue-500.rounded-full.h-7.w-7
                            img(src='/images/check.png' alt='')
                        h1.ml-3.font-bold.text-3xl &Idot;novasyon
                    p.text-gray-600.mt-3
                        | &Idot;nsanlar&imath;n ara&ccedil; sat&imath;n alma ve satma &scedil;eklini yeniden tasarlad&imath;k
                        | ve en iyi m&uuml;&scedil;teri deneyimini sunmak i&ccedil;in s&uuml;rekli &ccedil;al&imath;&scedil;&imath;yoruz.

